findings.title: Function _tokenTransfer send burn amount to dead address
findings.description: To burn properly, use decreasing rTotal and tTotal values instead of sending tokens to dead address.

findings.title: Owner can change the tax, burn, marketing and liquidity fees
findings.description: The contract owner has privileges to modify critical fee parameters, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change marketing addresses
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify marketing addresses.

findings.title: Owner can change the maximum transaction amount
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the maximum allowed transaction amount.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from the fee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude from the fee.
